            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Short version: mod_wsgi (and other production servers) just \"pick up\" the application object from your namespace. There shouldn't be any `app.run` involved, because `app.run` launches Flask's primitive dev server and nothing else.\n"
        },
